<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html charset=UTF-8" />
  <head>
    <title>KKBooks Email</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #e8f5e9; font-size: 14px">
    <table
      role="presentation"
      width="100%"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      border="0"
      style="background-color: #e8f5e9">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table
            role="presentation"
            width="600"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            border="0"
            style="
              background-color: #ffffff;
              border-radius: 8px;
              padding: 20px;
              font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
              color: #333;
            ">
            <tr>
              <td
                align="left"
                style="
                  padding: 15px 20px;
                  height: 60px;
                  border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
                  color: #ffffff;
                  font-size: 20px;
                  font-weight: bold;
                ">
                <img
                  src="https://uitbookstorestorage.blob.core.windows.net/images/logo.jpg"
                  alt="KKBooks Logo"
                  class="m_-999112447989606707logo CToWUd"
                  style="display: block; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; width: auto; height: auto"
                  data-bit="iit" />
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 20px; line-height: 1.6">
                {{ content }}
                <p style="margin: 10px 0; opacity: 0.8">
                  <i>**Email này được gửi tự động từ hệ thống. Vui lòng không trả lời email này**</i>
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td
                align="center"
                style="
                  padding: 20px;
                  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #01bf65, #7fd955);
                  color: #ffffff;
                  border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
                ">
                <p style="margin: 10px 0">
                  <a href="#" style="text-decoration: none; margin: 0 8px">
                    <img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/24/ffffff/facebook.png" alt="Facebook" />
                  </a>
                  <a href="#" style="text-decoration: none; margin: 0 8px">
                    <img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/24/ffffff/instagram-new.png" alt="Instagram" />
                  </a>
                  <a href="#" style="text-decoration: none; margin: 0 8px">
                    <img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/24/ffffff/twitter.png" alt="X (Twitter)" />
                  </a>
                  <a href="#" style="text-decoration: none; margin: 0 8px">
                    <img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/24/ffffff/link.png" alt="Website" />
                  </a>
                </p>

                <p style="margin: 5px 0">Email: <a href="mailto:support@bookstore.com">support@kkbooks.com.vn</a></p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0">Địa chỉ: Khu phố 6, P.Linh Trung, Tp.Thủ Đức, Tp.Hồ Chí Minh</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
